Any redistribution must retain this copyright notice and the full text of this License, without imposing additional restrictions.

2. 禁止商业用途 / Prohibition of Commercial Use

中文：
除非事先获得版权所有者的明确书面授权，严禁以任何形式将本软件或其衍生作品用于商业用途。

商业用途包括但不限于以下情形：

出售、出租、许可或转让本软件或其衍生作品；

将本软件用于任何收费系统、付费产品、订阅服务、SaaS 服务或其他盈利性项目；

因本软件提供收费的安装、部署、运维、咨询、培训或技术支持服务（即使软件本身免费）；

在企业、机构、组织或任何商业环境中使用本软件（包括但不限于内部系统、测试、PoC 或演示）；

基于本软件提供任何直接或间接产生经济收益的服务或解决方案。

English:
Unless explicitly authorized in writing by the copyright holder, any form of commercial use of this software or its derivative works is strictly prohibited.

Commercial use includes, but is not limited to:

Selling, leasing, licensing, or transferring this software or derivative works;

Using this software in any paid, monetized, subscription-based, SaaS, or revenue-generating product or service;

Charging fees for installation, deployment, operation, maintenance, consulting, training, or technical support related to this software (even if the software itself is provided free of charge);

Using this software in any corporate, institutional, organizational, or business environment, including internal systems, testing, proof-of-concept, or demonstrations;

Providing any service or solution that directly or indirectly generates revenue based on this software.

